Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-90,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a "guiding light." The entrance to\Nthe Grand Line lies ahead of that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to find the All Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to become\Na master swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to draw a world map!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-In order...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to become a brave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.66,0:02:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.67,0:02:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Precursor to a New Adventure!\NApis, a Mysterious Girl"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's meal time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone?! Hey! Where're you?!\NWhere're you hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's no use!\NIt's storming outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:02:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, you can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay put, we won't\Ndo anything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, calm down!\N--What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search the whole ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take her into custody\Nas soon as you find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still a child.\NDon't be rough on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's dangerous!\N--Come down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have the sail\Nunfurled like that in this storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please protect me, Grandpa Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What're you going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! It's dangerous! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots! What is this report?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl may be a clue to the Dragonite\Nthat I've spent years searching for!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you realize how serious this is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eric!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been here all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose a clue to the elixir of\Nimmortality after I've finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go join my fleet and find her\Nno matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all due respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tracking down someone\Nwasn't in the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you however much you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hired you for a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Losing a clue now will be a blow\Nfor you as well, will it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:06:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Your Excellency,\NCommodore Nelson Royal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Aren't we in the Grand Line yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just left Loguetown two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take a few more days.\NWait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nice weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That storm seems like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I see a flock of birds to starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A flock of birds?\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also see something\Nkind of big on the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see it well.\NI wonder what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Maybe a fish?\N--A small boat...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be a big fish, too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I often hear that\Nseabirds flock above fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Let's have them for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:06:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Now that's a stretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His body sure is convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty big!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on a second...\NWhat're you gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Sorry, Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbass!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna... cut him down... someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look. That's no fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is she a fishperson?\NWhere's her web?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot. Just how does\Nshe look like a fishperson?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was a little girl in\Na small boat like that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've come to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you're doing\Nbetter than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry.\NI'm cooking soup right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you in a ship wreck or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've been in big trouble.\NWhat's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you ask someone questions,\Nyou should give your name first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good point. My name is Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who's cooking soup\Nin the kitchen is Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one with a scary face\Nwearing a bellyband is Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who's unconscious\Nover there is Usopp. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy. I'm the captain\Nof this pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do with this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh, well, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's think about it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why? Why? Why in the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went through all that trouble and did\Nscary things to escape from the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all things, why did I get\Npicked up by a pirate ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'll think about\Nit after I eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never learn no matter\Nhow many times I tell you, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you get it\Nthrough your thick skull?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask, I'll make something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, like I told you,\Ndon't take food without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Aren't you eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't eat this afternoon, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you holding back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling ya, it's not\Npoisoned or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just sit there like that,\Nhe'll finish everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not eating, I'll eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Sanji's the cook I picked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never eaten anything this good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're finally smiling.\N--Oh, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're eating again, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't eat that much for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You emptied two pots, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.04,0:10:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got scared when you heard\Nwe're pirates, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's a natural reaction\Ntowards pirates these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're not gonna sell me off?\N--No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all evil-looking, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a right\Nto talk with that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:11:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have more, mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, this ship isn't the kind\Nof pirate ship you're thinking of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Another plate, please!\N--As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Me, too!\N--Do it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You meanie...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wo-oah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Wh-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Just what'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was preparing a meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Breakfast is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, breakfast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What breakfast explodes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You made this?\N--Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has quite... a unique appearance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! I'm digging in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition to rescuing me,\Nyou're feeding me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything to help you from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be helpful... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really edible?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop grumbling and just eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously, is it really safe to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's possible that\Njust the appearance is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Was it that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!\NI put in the wrong seasoning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's a common mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine if you\Nare careful next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she took the trouble\Nto prepare it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat every crumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't waste this\Ngirl's kindness. This girl's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's your name, by the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis! My name is Apis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis-chan put her heart into this food!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I won't allow anyone to waste food!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cook something\Nfor you later, Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm not good at cooking...\Nbut I wanted to be helpful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.\NWe really appreciate the thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the cooking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're many other things\Nthat you could help out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna eat barbecue next.\NI haven't had it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why were you\Ndrifting on the sea, Apis?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I escaped from a Navy ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From a Navy ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...during the stormy\Nnight three days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that small boat in such a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what'd you do in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had to escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which means you weren't on\Ntheir ship as a guest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then the Navy wouldn't\Ngo after every little villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well... uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you a super villain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! There's no way I'd do bad things!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never did bad things...\Nbut I can't tell you why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal?\NShe must have her reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she doesn't want to say,\Nthen we shouldn't press her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. But can you at\Nleast tell us where you're from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from Warship Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warship Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'll check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it called Warship Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because the shape of the\Nisland looks exactly like a warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! This is the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's close to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're around here right now,\Nso it's not that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What do you wanna do?\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna go\Nback to Warship Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep sailing like this,\Nwe are going to enter the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were nice enough to save me\Nand I feel bad burdening you further...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I want to go back to the island!\NI'm sorry. I'm selfish, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hand me to a ship heading\Nwest on your way if possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work things out on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, that's a real burden!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that a pirate ship can\Nget close to another ship so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:16:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since it's not totally out of our way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we're not really in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, what the heck?\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter either way to me.\NWhat should we do, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that sounds fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Grand Line isn't\Nthat far, either, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The island looks\Nlike a warship, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sounds like they've decided.\N--Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to stop\Nby Warship Island for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah.\N--All right! Thank you, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! All right! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To show my appreciation,\NI'll prepare lots of dishes every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ship sighted ahead at 13 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mid-size caravel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:16:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see a flag with a skull\Nmark on the main mast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't know their own station,\Nsailing around in the seas
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under Commodore Nelson's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they're just small fries.\NJust leave them alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. That flag doesn't\Nbelong to small fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly,\Nthat belongs to Straw Hat Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a man with a 30 million Berry\Nbounty on his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the ones people have\Nbeen talking about lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still can't find the girl\Neven with this big fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that someone has her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, pirates of that caliber...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it going to be a problem if you\Nleave them be, Lt. Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what this feeling is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I see ships\Napproaching from the rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--Ugh! Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They're Navy ships!\N--Navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not just\None or two ships, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's a fleet like that doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they after my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot even for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that they need that\Nmany to capture me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazing, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so easygoing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those ships belong to Branch 8!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I escaped from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...? There! I found her!\NI see the girl on their deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just as I said,\Nwasn't it, Lt. Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I hurt your pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you make a mistake\Nand lose that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the clue to the elixir\Nof immortality, the Dragonite,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.73,0:18:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how furious\NCommodore Nelson would get.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare the main cannons!\NWe'll capture that pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:19:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! They're firing at us!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention pirate ship!\NStop the ship immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were warning shots.\NThe next shots will hit your ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we'd stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do, Luffy? If you\Nwanna take 'em on, I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah. Why don't we?\N--Ahhh! W-Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys always like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the heck are you\Ngonna do against that fleet?!\N--Apis, go to the cabin downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We'll make a raid on them.\N--O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A raid isn't gonna work!\N--O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We'll make it work.\N--You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not saying you have to come.\NBack us up with the cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? So I'm staying on this ship?\NOkay, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--And we'll get clear\Nof them at full speed!\N--Hey, Apis. What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You take care of the rest.\N--Hey, Apis. What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You take care of the rest.\N--He said a wind is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A strong wind is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Lean the sail towards the south!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp and Sanji-kun,\Nright rudder full! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--O-Okay.\N--Yes, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gust is coming.\NWe'll ride it and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we fight them head on,\Nwe'll lose no matter how good we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can take them, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their ship shows no signs of stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're mocking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! The pirate ship sped up\Nand changed its route!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--They're heading south!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,South?! How foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they know what's in that direction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Lt. Commander?!\NGo after them! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! This is fast!\NThis is a good wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that, Luffy!\NThe Navy's falling behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! You guys're slow turtles!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good! We can't catch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Navy fleet falling behind\Nsuch a small ship? Dimwit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A small ship has better mobility!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna hear excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Commander, this ship will soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Lt. Commander!\N--I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop all the ships!\NPrepare to turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Lt. Commander!\NWhy are you stopping the ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep going,\Nwe'll go into the Calm Belt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So what? Go after them!\N--No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't appreciate the\Nseriousness of this matter, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't lose that girl now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you going to say\Nto Commodore Nelson?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm prepared to take the punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just sit by and let this fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my subordinates\Nbe swallowed by the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.69,0:21:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you say,\Nthe chase ends here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How... foolish...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy isn't following us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Captain Usopp\Nscare the pants off them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Amazing! Just as\Nyou'd expect from our navigator!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.04,0:21:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Nami-san. To think you\Ndetected such a wind beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.98,0:21:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was like an instinct, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nami-san is lovely\Nwhen she's humble, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.65,0:21:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, shall we head\Nstraight to Warship Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:21:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Really?!\N--Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! To Warship Island, let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.66,0:22:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had a serious look\Non your face for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.67,0:22:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I hope it's just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.34,0:22:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like this ship hasn't\Nbeen moving at all for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.01,0:22:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.01,0:22:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, the sail\Nisn't catching any wind at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.79,0:22:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.36,0:22:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.03,0:22:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've entered the Calm Belt!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.31,0:23:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the Calm Belt?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:24:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll head straight to Warship Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.48,0:24:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.65,0:24:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always makes us do reckless things!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.82,0:24:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, don't you think Apis\Nhas an air of secrecy about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.99,0:24:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at that!\NSomething incredible's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.32,0:24:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.66,0:24:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode on One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.99,0:24:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Miraculous Creature! Apis's Secret\Nand the Legendary Island."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.33,0:24:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
